[TITLE]
;;Project Title/Notes
Alternate 1 - Demonstrates the fix for a v5.1.013 bug that produced incorrect rainfall when the same time series was used by
one rain gage assigned to a Unit Hydrograph and another assigned to a subcatchment. The results for total RDII
volume and total watershed rainfall for this data set now match the correct values produced by release 5.1.012.

